description:
EastEnders.EXTRA.Back.To.Ours.Nitin.Ganatra.and.Himesh.Patel

Celebrate 30 years of EastEnders in the company of those who know it best - the stars! Relive iconic moments and find out the real gossip from the set.

Nitin & Himesh welcome you into their Walford home to celebrate 30 years of EastEnders. Relive classic Masood moments, fires, collapsing buildings, weddings and more!
